                                            <p class="h3">Updates to this privacy statement</p>

                                            <p>This Privacy Statement was last updated in September 2020. We reserve the right to update and change this Privacy Statement from time to time in order to reflect changes in the way in which we use your personal data or for changing legal requirements. Any amended Privacy Statement will apply from the date it is posted on RIT website or otherwise made available to you.</p>

